    "text": "Protecting Charitable Giving Act\n\nThis bill increases the penalty for the unauthorized disclosure of the identities of donors to tax-exempt organizations from a maximum of $5,000 to between $10,000 and $250,000. It\u00a0 also modifies venue rules to allow prosecution of offenses in the judicial district in which a victim of an offense resides."
